==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: electric chair
<hw>e*lec"tric chair`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a device used for
execution of criminals, consisting of a specially designed chair in
which the victim is killed by passing a large current of electricity
through the body. This method of killing is called
<usedfor>electrocution</usedfor>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> the chair, death chair, hot seat.</syn>
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>electrical charge</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>electric charge</ent>⟦br⟧
